      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "x": -1400.0874542116374,
      "y": 102.52932061706025,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "width": 1517.071044921875,
      "height": 908.4369330852559,
      "seed": 572647206,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775569678253,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 34.6071212603907,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "Functional Requirement -> users should be able to \n\n- Book tickets -> \n\n- View an event -> \n\n- Search for events\n\nNon-functional Requirements -> \n- low latency search \n- strong consistency for booking tickets & high availability for search and viewing events\n- read >> write\n- scalability to handle surges from popular events\n\n---------\nOut of scope:\n- GDPR compliance\n- fault tolerance \n- etc.  \n\nStep 2 Entities &   API ",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Functional Requirement -> users should be able to \n\n- Book tickets -> \n\n- View an event -> \n\n- Search for events\n\nNon-functional Requirements -> \n- low latency search \n- strong consistency for booking tickets & high availability for search and viewing events\n- read >> write\n- scalability to handle surges from popular events\n\n---------\nOut of scope:\n- GDPR compliance\n- fault tolerance \n- etc.  \n\nStep 2 Entities &   API ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
