      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775569678244,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "send_welcome_email.delay(user.id)\n\n👉 .delay() means:\n➡️ send to queue, don’t execute immediately\n\n🔥 Key Features\n✅ Asynchronous execution\n✅ Distributed workers (scale horizontally)\n✅ Retry mechanism\n✅ Scheduling (cron-like via Celery Beat)\n✅ Task prioritization",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "send_welcome_email.delay(user.id)\n\n👉 .delay() means:\n➡️ send to queue, don’t execute immediately\n\n🔥 Key Features\n✅ Asynchronous execution\n✅ Distributed workers (scale horizontally)\n✅ Retry mechanism\n✅ Scheduling (cron-like via Celery Beat)\n✅ Task prioritization",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
