      "text": "For extracting PDF we will use pdfplumber library\n\npip install pdfplumber\n\n\nFor creating text to pdf we can use pdfkit library\n    pip install pdfkit\n    for ubuntu ->\n        sudo apt-get install wkhtmltopdf\n    for mac -> \n        brew install homebrew/cask/wkhtmltopdf",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "For extracting PDF we will use pdfplumber library\n\npip install pdfplumber\n\n\nFor creating text to pdf we can use pdfkit library\n    pip install pdfkit\n    for ubuntu ->\n        sudo apt-get install wkhtmltopdf\n    for mac -> \n        brew install homebrew/cask/wkhtmltopdf",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
